# Composables Context

When working with files in `src/composables/`, read `documentation/composables-and-state.md` for:
- All composables: useState, useI18n/t/l, useHotkeys, useAlert/useConfirm/useMessage, usePopup, useCopy, useSelect
- State management pattern: provide/inject from root UmoEditor component, localStorage via useStorage
- All composables are auto-imported — no explicit import needed
- Vue and VueUse exports are also auto-imported
